publications.citation: Lein, E.S. et al. (2007) Genome-wide atlas of gene expression in the adult mouse brain, Nature 445: 168-176.

properties.name: Allen Mouse Brain Atlas
properties.description: The Allen Mouse Brain Atlas includes a full-color, high-resolution anatomical reference atlas accompanied by a systematic, hierarchically organized taxonomy of mouse brain structures. Anatomical annotations in classical histological atlas plates were extracted to create a comprehensive volumetric reference atlas of the mouse brain.
